---
---

<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Sobre mí — Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      :root {
        --cream: #f7f2ec;
        --terracota: #b85c38;
        --terracota-light: #e8d5c4;
        --terracota-dark: #5c3d2e;
        --text: #2a1f1a;
        --muted: #8a6f5e;
        --serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
        --sans: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
      }

      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
      body { background: var(--cream); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--sans); font-weight: 300; }

      nav {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        z-index: 100;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 1.25rem 3rem;
        background: var(--cream);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--terracota-light);
      }

      .nav-logo {
        font-family: var(--serif);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: var(--terracota-dark);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }

      .nav-links a {
        font-family: var(--sans);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: var(--terracota); }

      .page {
        padding: 12rem 3rem 6rem;
        max-width: 900px;
      }

      .page-label {
        font-family: var(--sans);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.1s;
      }

      .page-title {
        font-family: var(--serif);
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1;
        color: var(--terracota-dark);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.2s;
      }

      .page-title em {
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--terracota);
      }

      .content {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 4rem;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.4s;
      }

      .bio p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--text);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .bio p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

      .sidebar h3 {
        font-family: var(--sans);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--terracota-light);
      }

      .skills {
        list-style: none;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }

      .skills li {
        font-family: var(--serif);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: var(--terracota-dark);
        padding: 0.4rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--terracota-light);
      }

      footer {
        padding: 2rem 3rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--terracota-light);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-top: 6rem;
      }

      @keyframes fadeUp {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
        to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
        .page { padding: 10rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Nombre Apellido</a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Trabajo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/sobre-mi" class="active">Sobre mí</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contacto">Contacto</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <main class="page">
      <p class="page-label">Quién soy</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">Sobre <em>mí</em></h1>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="bio">
          <p>Placeholder — Párrafo de presentación. Quién eres, de dónde vienes, qué te mueve. Escríbelo en primera persona y con naturalidad.</p>
          <p>Placeholder — Cuéntalo que conecta tus disciplinas: el diseño gráfico, la música y los videojuegos no son mundos separados para ti, sino formas distintas de explorar lo mismo.</p>
          <p>Placeholder — Un detalle personal o una forma de trabajar que te define.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar">
          <h3>Disciplinas</h3>
          <ul class="skills">
            <li>Diseño Gráfico</li>
            <li>Identidad Visual</li>
            <li>Producción Musical</li>
            <li>Diseño de Videojuegos</li>
            <li>Dirección de Arte</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Herramientas</h3>
          <ul class="skills">
            <li>Figma / Illustrator</li>
            <li>Ableton Live</li>
            <li>Unity / Godot</li>
            <li>HTML · CSS · JS</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <span>Nombre Apellido</span>
      <span>contacto@email.com</span>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
